description:
Redevelopment of 6 no. blocks by whole or (in the case of the corner block with shops) part demolition and rebuilding to provide four storey replacement blocks consisting of 79 residential units and associated provisions for parking, vehicular and pedestrian circulation and landscaping. 

 APPLICANT'S PLAN NOS.:  3226DE/1A, 2A, 9A, 16A, 17, 18, 19,                         20, 21, 22, 23, 24, 25
decision_conditions:
CONDITION: The development hereby permitted shall be begun not later than the expiration of five years from the date of this permission. 

 REASON: To comply with the provisions of Section 91(1) of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
